BY EARLY MORNING, THEY WERE

03:06.887 --> 03:08.989
ACROSS THE BORDER AND WAITING

03:08.989 --> 03:10.524
PATIENTLY FOR A TRAIN THAT WOULD

03:10.524 --> 03:12.726
TAKE THEM WEST OR NORTH.

