THE INHABITANTS OF THE BORDER

03:17.097 --> 03:18.598
TOWN OF NICKELSDORF HAD LAID OUT

03:18.598 --> 03:20.333
FOOD, DRINK, EVEN A SELECTION OF

03:20.333 --> 03:22.602
SECONDHAND CLOTHING.

