IN SMALL, WELL-ORGANIZED GROUPS,

03:24.805 --> 03:26.339
FAMILIES FIRST, THEY WERE

03:26.339 --> 03:28.208
ALLOWED ON TO A TRAIN, THIS ONE

03:28.208 --> 03:30.343
TO VIENNA.

