IN THEIR EXCITEMENT, SOME RAN TO

03:31.845 --> 03:33.580
THE CARRIAGES, ALTHOUGH, IN

03:33.580 --> 03:35.982
TRUTH, THERE WAS LITTLE NEED.

03:35.982 --> 03:36.550
>> THANK YOU.

03:36.550 --> 03:39.319
VERY, VERY HAPPY.

03:39.319 --> 03:40.087
>> Reporter: BACK IN HUNGARY,

03:40.087 --> 03:41.788
THERE ARE MANY THOUSANDS MORE

