THAT MAY NOT BE ENOUGH.

03:47.294 --> 03:48.328
THIS MORNING, NOT PREPARED TO

03:48.328 --> 03:50.030
WAIT, ANOTHER GROUP SET OFF TO

03:50.030 --> 03:51.798
WALK TO THE BORDER, THOUGH THIS

03:51.798 --> 03:53.400
TIME THEY MAY NOT HAVE TO TRUDGE

03:53.400 --> 03:55.268
AS FAR.

