04:24.898 --> 04:26.666
IN SWEDEN TOLD HIM ABOUT HIS

04:26.666 --> 04:28.301
JOURNEY ACROSS THE MEDITERRANEAN

04:28.301 --> 04:30.904
SEA, LEAVING HIS FAMILY BEHIND.

