SO, THERE ARE MANY PARENTS

05:26.326 --> 05:28.461
TAKING THE DECISION THAT IT'S

05:28.461 --> 05:30.363
NOT WORTH RISKING THEIR

05:30.363 --> 05:32.199
CHILDREN'S LIVES, AND THEY'RE

05:32.199 --> 05:33.333
LEAVING THEM BEHIND AND THEY'RE

05:33.333 --> 05:35.468
COMING TO COUNTRIES WHERE'S THEY

05:35.468 --> 05:36.870
HOPE THERE WILL BE A GOOD FAMILY

05:36.870 --> 05:38.672
REUNIFICATION POLICY, AS

05:38.672 --> 05:39.506
SWEDEN HAS.

