>> I THINK THERE ARE TWO THINGS,

05:52.052 --> 05:54.020
AS FAR AS WE CAN SEE, REALLY.

05:54.020 --> 05:55.455
RIGHT NOW, IT'S THE END OF THE

05:55.455 --> 05:57.657
SUMMER, AND THE MEDITERRANEAN

05:57.657 --> 05:58.892
SUDDENLY CHANGES FROM BEING A

05:58.892 --> 06:00.060
FAIRLY BENEVOLENT SEA AS IT HAS

06:00.060 --> 06:01.428
BEEN IN THE PAST THREE MONTHS

06:01.428 --> 06:02.862
INTO SOMETHING THAT IS VERY

06:02.862 --> 06:04.631
PERILOUS INDEED.

06:04.631 --> 06:06.833
THERE'S A WIND THAT BLOWS IN

06:06.833 --> 06:09.803
SEPTEMBER THAT CREATES WINDS OF

06:09.803 --> 06:12.005
FORCE 8-10, AND IT'S EXTREMELY

06:12.005 --> 06:12.772
DANGEROUS.

06:12.772 --> 06:13.673
EVEN JUST FOR THE THREE MILES

