THERE IS A RUSH TO GET ACROSS

06:25.585 --> 06:27.220
BEFORE THE WEATHER CHANGES.

06:27.220 --> 06:28.989
BUT, ALSO, PEOPLE I HAVE BEEN

06:28.989 --> 06:30.290
SPEAKING TO ON LESBOS, ONE OF

06:30.290 --> 06:33.260
THE MAIN ISLANDS THAT THE PEOPLE

06:33.260 --> 06:34.527
COME TO IN GREECE, THEY'RE

06:34.527 --> 06:35.862
SAYING WHAT WE'RE HEARING FROM

06:35.862 --> 06:37.163
THE SYRIANS IS THAT THE

06:37.163 --> 06:38.398
SITUATION INSIDE DAMASCUS, THE

06:38.398 --> 06:40.300
SYRIAN CAPITAL, IS BECOMING VERY

06:40.300 --> 06:41.968
GRAVE, INDEED, AND THERE IS AN

06:41.968 --> 06:42.669
IMPERATIVE TO GET OUT.

06:42.669 --> 06:44.437
MAYBE THERE IS SOMETHING

06:44.437 --> 06:45.538
HAPPENING ON THE VARIOUS

06:45.538 --> 06:47.073
WARFRONTS THERE THAT IS DRIVING

06:47.073 --> 06:48.608
PEOPLE OUT.

06:48.608 --> 06:51.478
ALL OF THE REFUGEES THAT YOU

06:51.478 --> 06:53.513
TALK TO ON THE VARIOUS STAGES OF

06:53.513 --> 06:54.781
THE ROUTE, THEY'RE ALL IN TOUCH

06:54.781 --> 06:56.416
WITH EACH OTHER.

06:56.416 --> 06:57.584
THEY KNOW WHICH PLACES ARE-- YOU

06:57.584 --> 06:59.352
KNOW, THE WAYS TO GO.

