KNOW, THEY MUST BE SORT OF ABLE

07:03.256 --> 07:04.524
TO READ THE RUNES TO SEE EUROPE

07:04.524 --> 07:07.160
IS WAVERING AT THE MOMENT.

07:07.160 --> 07:08.695
COUNTRIES DON'T WANT TO BE ON

07:08.695 --> 07:10.063
THE WRONG SIDE OF HISTORY

07:10.063 --> 07:11.331
BECAUSE THIS IS A VERY EMOTIONAL

07:11.331 --> 07:12.966
TIME FOR PEOPLE, ESPECIALLY

07:12.966 --> 07:14.501
AFTER THE PUBLICATION OF THAT

07:14.501 --> 07:16.403
TERRIBLE PICTURE OF THE LITTLE

07:16.403 --> 07:19.039
BOY WHO DROWNED IN BODRUM.

