FOLKS WHO WERE BUSINESSMEN-- AND

07:21.941 --> 07:22.976
FROM OTHER STORIES THAT I'VE

07:22.976 --> 07:24.077
READ, THERE SEEMS TO BE A

07:24.077 --> 07:25.512
MIDDLE-CLASS AND UPPER-MIDDLE-

07:25.512 --> 07:27.814
CLASS MOVEMENT HERE OF PEOPLE

