WHY ARE THEY FINALLY DECIDING TO

07:31.184 --> 07:32.319
LEAVE?

07:32.319 --> 07:33.753
WHY DID THEY STAY IN PLACE?

07:33.753 --> 07:34.754
AND, TWO, WHAT DOES THIS MEAN

07:34.754 --> 07:36.222
FOR PEOPLE WHO DON'T HAVE MONEY

07:36.222 --> 07:38.758
TO GET OUT?

07:38.758 --> 07:39.759
>> THE ONE THING THAT IS REALLY

07:39.759 --> 07:40.694
QUITE NOTICEABLE, ACTUALLY, IS

07:40.694 --> 07:42.495
THAT ON THE ROAD, THE PEOPLE WHO

07:42.495 --> 07:43.496
DO SEEM TO HAVE MONEY ARE

